      <title>特朗普胜选刺激消费，印度 IT 股表现突出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/india-s-it-stocks-stand-out-as-trump-win-boosts-spending-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的回归引发了对美元走强和技术外包增加的预期，印度大型 IT 服务提供商的股价在近期上涨之后有望进一步上涨，抵消了其他行业的疲软人气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/india-s-it-stocks-stand-out-as-trump-win-boosts-spending-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 05:16:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sea 股价上涨 430 亿美元，获利引来分析师看涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/sea-s-profit-draws-bullish-analyst-calls-after-43-billion-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sea Ltd. 在电子商务领域重获盈利，令分析师对其股价更加看好，今年迄今其市值已上涨 430 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/sea-s-profit-draws-bullish-analyst-calls-after-43-billion-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 05:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税争端导致中国电动汽车制造商在欧洲销量进一步下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/chinese-ev-makers-slip-further-in-europe-amid-tariff-tussles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国汽车制造商进军欧洲电动汽车市场的努力继续遭遇阻力，在新关税实施前夕，10 月份其对欧洲电动汽车市场的交付份额出现下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/chinese-ev-makers-slip-further-in-europe-amid-tariff-tussles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大反垄断监管机构起诉谷歌，寻求拆分广告技术业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/canada-antitrust-watchdog-sues-google-seeking-ad-tech-breakup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大反垄断监管机构正在将 Alphabet Inc. 的谷歌告上法庭，指控其滥用网络广告市场支配地位，这给这家搜索巨头带来了更多法律挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/canada-antitrust-watchdog-sues-google-seeking-ad-tech-breakup</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 21:05:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 和 Meta 做好应对澳大利亚社交媒体禁令后果的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/tiktok-meta-brace-for-fallout-from-australia-s-social-media-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚出台了有争议的新法律，禁止 16 岁以下儿童使用社交媒体，这是迄今为止对 Facebook 和 TikTok 等平台实施的最严厉打击之一，目前世界各国政府都在想方设法保护儿童免受有害内容的侵害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/tiktok-meta-brace-for-fallout-from-australia-s-social-media-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 20:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国政府计划提供约 20 亿欧元新芯片补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/german-government-plans-about-2-billion-in-new-chip-subsidies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两个月前，英特尔公司搁置了在马格德堡建设价值 300 亿欧元（320 亿美元）芯片工厂的计划。目前，德国政府正准备向该国半导体行业注入数十亿欧元的新投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/german-government-plans-about-2-billion-in-new-chip-subsidies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 17:14:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷诺在华大举招聘，推动本土电动汽车发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/renault-goes-on-china-hiring-spree-to-bolster-ev-push-at-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在需求疲软的情况下，雷诺公司正试图通过扩大其甚至不销售汽车的国家——中国——的影响力来加强其电动汽车业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/renault-goes-on-china-hiring-spree-to-bolster-ev-push-at-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 16:31:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌支持的 R2 通过股权和债务融资筹集 5900 万美元用于借贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/google-backed-r2-raises-59-million-in-equity-debt-for-lending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[R2 是一家拉丁美洲初创公司，为该地区的科技公司提供借贷工具，该公司通过股权和债务融资了 5900 万美元，以继续扩大业务，包括推动其在智利的业务增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/google-backed-r2-raises-59-million-in-equity-debt-for-lending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可与 Pele Green 达成 1.16 亿美元太阳能发电厂协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/glencore-makes-deal-with-pele-green-for-116-million-solar-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可股份有限公司 (Glencore Plc) 的南非铁合金部门及其合资伙伴 Merafe Resources Ltd. 与 Pele Green Energy 达成协议，建设一座价值 21 亿兰特（1.16 亿美元）的公用事业规模可再生能源工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/glencore-makes-deal-with-pele-green-for-116-million-solar-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 15:57:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国流行音乐明星纷纷退出 Hybe，引发强烈抗议，导致工作室股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/k-pop-group-newjeans-says-they-will-split-from-agency-hybe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国流行音乐超级明星 NewJeans 终止了与 Hybe Co. 的合作，此举引发了一场前所未有的、震惊韩国的骚乱，导致该工作室的市值在周五缩水了 7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/k-pop-group-newjeans-says-they-will-split-from-agency-hybe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 12:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
